## Features Implemented

| Feature | Status |
|---|---|
| JWT auth (login/register/role-based) | ✅ |
| Admin: Dashboard with 6 stat cards | ✅ |
| Admin: CRUD Companies + approve/reject/blacklist | ✅ |
| Admin: CRUD Students + search/blacklist | ✅ |
| Admin: CRUD Drives + approve/close | ✅ |
| Admin: Applications with drive/student/status filtering | ✅ |
| Admin: Reports with Chart.js charts | ✅ |
| Company: Registration with pending approval | ✅ |
| Company: Create/edit/delete drives (gated by approval) | ✅ |
| Company: View/manage applications per drive | ✅ |
| Company: Schedule/manage interviews | ✅ |
| Company: Update application status (shortlist→selected) | ✅ |
| Student: Browse approved drives with search | ✅ |
| Student: Eligibility validation before apply | ✅ |
| Student: Duplicate application prevention | ✅ |
| Student: View applications + interview details | ✅ |
| Student: Placement history | ✅ |
| Student: Profile edit + resume upload | ✅ |
| Student: CSV export (async with fallback) | ✅ |
| Celery: Daily reminders | ✅ |
| Celery: Monthly HTML report | ✅ |
| Redis caching (with SimpleCache fallback) | ✅ |

